Package: statfinr
Type: Package
Title: API Interface For Statistics Finland
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Oliver Saal
Maintainer: Oliver Saal <29450366+osaal@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Package for interfacing with the Statistics Finland API.
    This package is a wrapper for the Statistics Finland PXWeb API.
    It allows the user to explore the Statistics Finland databases from within R and request data in an R-friendly format.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
